Description
AutoSub helps you create add subtitles to your videos easily! It uses AI to generate the subtitles automatically which you can customise to your needs. This is not only for captions, you can edit your videos with it as well! Add backgrounds, crop, or rotate your videos and adjust them to your needs. Easily customize the background as blurred, gradient or a solid color, add animated texts and emojis, and post full-size videos on Instagram, Twitter, Facebook, Pinterest or Youtube easier than ever!
FEATURES
*Automatically create subtitles
*Customize the color, size, font, position and style of your subtitles
* Generate square videos - Import your videos and place them into the square Instagram layout without ever losing any of the footage!
* Multiple aspect ratios support
* Change the Background - solid color, gradient, image or blurred
* Add Captions - Add as many labels as you want, select their appearance timing and animation style
* Save HD videos to your Camera Roll
* Built-in Facebook, Instagram, Twitter, & Youtube support
Terms of Use: http://matekovacs.com/AutoSub/
AutoSub Pro Subscription:
The app includes a 1 month long auto-renewable subscription with a 3-day free trial, which will unlock premium features and costs $9.99/ month. It will be charged to your credit card through your iTunes account and will automatically renew unless you canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Any unused portion of a free trial period​ will be forfeited when you purchase the subscription. Though your subscription for the current month cannot be canceled, you can turn auto-renewal off in your account settings after purchase. See instructions here:
https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT202039
You can read the terms of use and privacy policy here: http://matekovacs.com/AutoSub/
